data.description: As you step into this beautifully maintained home, you'll be greeted by a sense of warmth and sophistication. The master bedroom suite addition, complete with new flooring, is a true sanctuary, offering the perfect retreat after a long day. With spacious living areas and generously sized bedrooms, you'll have all the space you need to create lasting memories with family and friends. New flooring has also been installed in the family room and kitchen, adding a touch of modern elegance to your living spaces. The convenience of two full baths and one half bath ensures everyone's comfort and ease of living.  This home has been meticulously cared for, boasting a new HVAC system, furnace, storm doors, roof, gutters, garage door, and most of the windows have been replaced - ensuring your peace of mind and keeping your energy bills in check.  The exterior of this property is a true oasis with a park-like yard that is fully fenced for your privacy and enjoyment. The addition of a new shed and an expanded driveway provides ample storage space for your outdoor equipment and room for all your vehicles.  Nestled on a quiet street, this home offers a peaceful and private setting while being conveniently located close to major roads, making your daily commute a breeze. Warwick Township's serene ambiance, coupled with the highly acclaimed Central Bucks School District, makes this an exceptional opportunity for families looking to settle into a wonderful community.  Don't miss the chance to make this stunning Warwick Township property your new home. Contact us today to schedule a private tour and discover the endless possibilities that await you in this beautiful residence.
